                                                                 pencil = simple SimHub property picker, ƒₓ = SimHub's
                                                                 own NCalc/js: formula dialog (BindingEditor). -->
                                                            <Button Grid.Column="2"
                                                                    Click="MBoosterEditFormula_Click"
                                                                    Tag="{Binding}"
                                                                    ToolTip="{x:Static res:Strings.Tooltip_EditMapping}"
